    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it a criminal offence to drive a noisy vehicle early morning or late night.",
        "additional_details": "Benefits:\r\n- Reduced incidences of health problems caused by lack of sleep and stress - hence money saved by the NHS\r\n- Greater feeling of community spirit and consideration in built-up environments\r\n- Doesn't prevent the ownership or use of noisy vehicles, just tighter controls over the times and areas they can be used\r\n- Punishes drivers who specifically aim to disrupt peaceful environments",
        "background": "'Noisy vehicles' includes drivers playing loud music from cars, as well as inherently loud motorbikes and tuned cars.\r\n\r\nThis petition aims to support the use of noise cameras and other police-controlled means to deter and find drivers of noisy vehicles in residential areas at set times.",
